    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我梳理一下：起点到Closed，Closed通过push事件转到Opening，Opening直接到Open，然后Open通过release转到Closing，Closing再回到Closed。另外Open还能直接到终点，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Closed",
