        "push"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，我觉得Closing到Closed的箭头方向我刚才说反了？不对，Closing之后确实是回到Closed，这个没错。但Open到终点的箭头要保留，表示任务完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Closing",
        "Closed",
        "Open",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Closing指向Closed，不是指向Opening。然后Open指向终点[*]。我检查一下刚才画的，Closing确实连回了Closed，没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Closing",
        "Closed",
        "Open",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了。整个流程就是：初始关闭→按push正在打开→完全打开→按release正在关闭→回到关闭，或者打开后直接结束。",
